<item>
            <title>[PIG-3484] Make the size of pig.script property configurable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3484</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Some applications (e.g. Lipstick) use the pig.script property to display the script. But since its size is limited by a hard-coded max, it&apos;s not always possible to store an entire script.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be nicer if the size of pig.script is configurable.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12670635">PIG-3484</key>
            <summary>Make the size of pig.script property configurable</summary>
